0xC67DB108A9ADE3BE// ForceSubmarineNeurtalBuoyancy
void FORCE_SUBMARINE_NEURTAL_BUOYANCY(Vehicle submarine, int time);Parameters:submarine: The submarine vehicle to apply neutral buoyancy to.time: The duration in milliseconds for which to maintain neutral buoyancy.Forces a submarine to maintain neutral buoyancy for a specified duration, preventing it from rising when unoccupied or without a driver.NativeDB Introduced: v2189
